Every 200 draws guarantees 1 Gold outfit. Every 50 draws guarantees 1 Silver outfit.
If both the Gold and Silver guarantees are triggered, the Silver guarantee shall trigger in the next draw.You will not get a gold outfit again until all gold outfits have been drawn.
